snippet.title: Spirit Hunters: Infinite Horde - Teaser Trailer (March 2022)
snippet.description:
Spirit Hunters: Infinite Horde - Teaser Trailer. Coming Spring 2022!

This teaser trailer is comprised of pre release content and is likely to change. 

You are the Spirit Hunters in this action rogue-lite. Slay huge waves of monsters and harvest their souls for ever increasing power. Unlock many playable characters, abilities, maps and more through a deep progression system. 

Follow us to learn more at...
Discord - https://discord.gg/DRHPUXPtEs
Twitter - https://twitter.com/CreatureCauldrn
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/creature_cauldron/
Tiktok - https://www.tiktok.com/@creaturecauldron
Website - https://www.creaturecauldrongames.com/
